---
import dennisPortrait from '../assets/artist/dennis-studio.jpeg';
---

<div class="about" id="about">

  <div class="about-image" data-reveal>
    <img src={dennisPortrait.src} alt="Portrait of Dennis Schneider" />
  </div>
<br>
  <div class="about-copy" data-reveal>
    <p class="about-label" data-i18n="aboutLabel">Mastery in Blonde</p>

    <h2 data-i18n="aboutHeadline">Blonde is not a color. It’s precision.</h2>

    <p>
      Hi, I'm Dennis – a self-employed master hairdresser and blonde specialist in Berlin Friedrichshain. For over 16 years, I've specialized in bleaching, balayage, lived-in looks, and natural, multidimensional hair color. If you're looking for a blonde expert in Berlin who combines high-quality results with healthy hair, you've come to the right place.
    </p>
<br>
    <p>
      My focus is on modern techniques that allow for smooth transitions, clear blonde tones, and perfect nuances – all without compromising hair quality. Every color treatment is individually tailored to your hair type, your daily routine, and your long-term hair structure. I work with professional brands such as Olaplex, Evo Hair, Danger Jones and other high-performance products to guarantee you long-lasting, healthy and vibrant color results. Whether it's bleaching, balayage, root coloring, glossing or a complete color transformation: my goal is for you to leave my chair with a look that suits you – modern, individual and effortless.
    </p>
<br>
    <p data-i18n="aboutCopy">
      Dennis Schneider is a Berlin-based master hairstylist and blonde specialist. From Friedrichshain, he builds natural, multi-dimensional blondes with a calm, considered approach.
    </p>

    <ul data-i18n-list="aboutList">
      <li>16+ years shaping blondes and lived-in color.</li>
      <li>Every result is tailored to hair type, lifestyle, and long-term health.</li>
      <li>No one-size-fits-all coloring. Only subtle luxury and clean transitions.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>


</div>

<style>
  .about-label  {
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--muted, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7));
  }

  .about {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
    align-items: start; /* 👈 prevents weird vertical centering with 100vh */
    padding: 4rem 1.5rem;
  }

  .about-copy {
    max-width: 42rem;
  }

  .about-copy h2 {
    margin: 0 0 1.2rem;
    font-family: Georgia, "Times New Roman", serif;
    font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 3vw, 3.5rem);
    line-height: 1.02;
  }

  .about-copy ul {
    margin: 1.5rem 0 0;
    padding-left: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--text-soft);
    list-style: disc;
  }

.about-copy li::marker {
  color: var(--border);
}

  .about-copy li {
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .about-image {
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    height: 100vh; /* 👈 full browser height */
  }

.about-copy p {
  text-align: justify;
  hyphens: auto;
}

  .about-image img {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .about {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
      padding: 3rem 1rem;
    }

    .about-copy {
      max-width: none;
    }

    .about-image {
      height: 60vh; /* 👈 more reasonable on tablets */
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .about-copy h2 {
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 6vw, 2.6rem);
    }

    .about-image {
      border-radius: 0.75rem;
      height: 50vh; /* 👈 avoids huge image on small screens */
    }


.about-copy {
  background: var(--surface-glass);
  padding: 2rem;
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
   border-radius: 1rem;
}

  }
</style>